            "value": "The inclusion criteria are :  - Diagnosis of AS based on (i) electron microscopic examination of the renal biopsy and/or (ii) molecular studies and/or (iii) abnormal expression of type IV collagen chains on skin and/or glomerular basement membranes. - Signed informed consent  "
